c: 29
v: 52
t: "ql: kfa biallah bayni wabaynakum shahdana ealaa sdqy 'aniy rswlh, waealaa tkdhybkm li wrdkm alhaqi aladhi jyt bih min eind allh, yaelam ma fi alsmwat walard, fala yakhfaa ealayh shay' fyhma. waladhin amanuu bialbatil wakafaruu biallah -me hadhih aldlayl alwadht- 'uwlayik hum alkhasirun fi aldunya walakhrt"